{"tid":443211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好驚鄰居會發生血案？","createTime":"2017-10-21T11:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T12:12:55.000Z","uid":68002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"478a085eefabf45af34b30e71030b7a65ee67c42","tid":443211,"uid":68002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:52:13.000Z","msg":"我隔離屋個呀婆同佢個仔一家一齊住，個婆有老人癡呆，成日唔記得自己做左咩（例如食左藥又話自己未食，唔見野又會話人偷野），佢個仔呢幾年開始頂唔順。<br />\n佢開始會罵呀婆罵到半層樓都聽到，個頻率重愈黎愈高（一晚幾次），呀仔啲老婆仔女都唔會出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個仔呢排重開始罵呀婆你去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始懷疑佢個仔有躁狂症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為幾年鄰居，唔想到有日血案發生先後悔，應該點做？"},{"pid":"aa72a09f91f75e2da249593622d82627f56403c8","tid":443211,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"先下手為強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3cfa058138da7c7e7329b2a9866c198ea2c016","tid":443211,"uid":68002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先下手為強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8c363c7f33bbc1d55bb458d82981e92deb717b","tid":443211,"uid":68002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:58:17.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf1370f8b0a96bfd89a337e8723a3df944a3a72","tid":443211,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先下手為強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkg